   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">To convert the alarm signals sent from the system to DNP3, a HU250
communication gateway is used. The HU250 gateway converts the Modbus
TCP/IP signal sent from the network management card (NMC).</p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">The NMC card is required for using the HU250 communication gateway.
The connection between the NMC and the HU250 uses a straight Ethernet
cable (RJ45 connection).</p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">A connection can then be made to the HU250 gateway with a straight
Ethernet cable (RJ45 connection) to access the DNP3 signals.</p>
